{
  "tts": [
    {
      "id": "a1",
      "text": "家帰って冷蔵庫開けたら",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 0,
      "endFrame": 82
    },
    {
      "id": "a2",
      "text": "あれ！？なにこれ…",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 83,
      "endFrame": 138
    },
    {
      "id": "a3",
      "text": "買った覚えのないケーキ箱発見",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 139,
      "endFrame": 332
    },
    {
      "id": "a4",
      "text": "いやけど誕生日誰もいねぇよな？",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 333,
      "endFrame": 405
    },
    {
      "id": "a5",
      "text": "って思いつつ中を見ると",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 406,
      "endFrame": 485
    },
    {
      "id": "a6",
      "text": "ハッピーバースデー私！",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 486,
      "endFrame": 564
    },
    {
      "id": "a7",
      "text": "って書かれた誕生日ケーキ",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 565,
      "endFrame": 706
    },
    {
      "id": "a8",
      "text": "ん！？え！？私！？ん！？",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 707,
      "endFrame": 792
    },
    {
      "id": "a9",
      "text": "って困惑してたら",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 793,
      "endFrame": 920
    },
    {
      "id": "a10",
      "text": "あ！帰ってたの！？おかえりぃぃぃ！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 921,
      "endFrame": 983
    },
    {
      "id": "a11",
      "text": "風呂上がりの妻がニッコニコで声かけてきて",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 984,
      "endFrame": 1087
    },
    {
      "id": "a12",
      "text": "あ！それ今から食べよ！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 1088,
      "endFrame": 1179
    },
    {
      "id": "a13",
      "text": "もう私の楽しみにしてたんだぁああ！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 1180,
      "endFrame": 1237
    },
    {
      "id": "a14",
      "text": "ってやっぱ妻のケーキだったので",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 1238,
      "endFrame": 1368
    },
    {
      "id": "a15",
      "text": "じゃあ僕が準備するから主役は座ってて",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 1369,
      "endFrame": 1448
    },
    {
      "id": "a16",
      "text": "いいの！？やったぁああ！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 1449,
      "endFrame": 1523
    },
    {
      "id": "a17",
      "text": "って飲み物に皿準備して一応ろうそくあったからケーキにさして",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 1524,
      "endFrame": 1724
    },
    {
      "id": "a18",
      "text": "ハッピーバースディートゥーユー",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 1725,
      "endFrame": 1799
    },
    {
      "id": "a19",
      "text": "ハッピーバースディートゥーユーディア嫁子〜",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 1800,
      "endFrame": 1962
    },
    {
      "id": "a20",
      "text": "いえーい！ありがとぉおおおお！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 1963,
      "endFrame": 2053
    },
    {
      "id": "a21",
      "text": "って全然誕生日でもなかったけど",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 2054,
      "endFrame": 2175
    },
    {
      "id": "a22",
      "text": "妻ならそうして欲しいかなって",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 2176,
      "endFrame": 2325
    },
    {
      "id": "a23",
      "text": "ノリノリで一緒にケーキを食べた",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 2326,
      "endFrame": 2458
    },
    {
      "id": "a24",
      "text": "なんで誕生日ケーキか気にならないの？",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 2459,
      "endFrame": 2550
    },
    {
      "id": "a25",
      "text": "って聞いたので",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 2551,
      "endFrame": 2607
    },
    {
      "id": "a26",
      "text": "お祝い事に理由とか要らなくない？",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 2608,
      "endFrame": 2719
    },
    {
      "id": "a27",
      "text": "って言ったら",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 2720,
      "endFrame": 2791
    },
    {
      "id": "a28",
      "text": "私さ、仕事できなくて",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 2792,
      "endFrame": 2892
    },
    {
      "id": "a29",
      "text": "そしたら俊君が仕事に言ってる間誰とも話さないんだ",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 2893,
      "endFrame": 3007
    },
    {
      "id": "a30",
      "text": "それが辛くて今日散歩行ったらさ、なんか誰かに祝ってもらいたいって言うか…",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 3008,
      "endFrame": 3067
    },
    {
      "id": "a31",
      "text": "なんかそんな感じ！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 3068,
      "endFrame": 3194
    },
    {
      "id": "a32",
      "text": "明日から頑張るから！ありがとね！",
      "speaker": "character2",
      "startFrame": 3195,
      "endFrame": 3290
    },
    {
      "id": "a33",
      "text": "いつでもお祝い事大歓迎だよ",
      "speaker": "character1",
      "startFrame": 3291,
      "endFrame": 3397
    },
    {
      "id": "a34",
      "text": "って翌日朝も２人で胸やけしながら残りのケーキを食べた",
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "startFrame": 3398,
      "endFrame": 3471
    }
  ],
